PKGBUILDS is a collection of Archlinux package descriptions.

To install a package e.g. maven3, download the collection or clone the repository.

* wget --no-check-certificate https://github.com/slopjong/PKGBUILDS/tarball/master -O SLOPBUILDS.tar.gz
* git clone --depth 1 git://github.com/slopjong/PKGBUILDS.git SLOPBUILDS

Change into the directory of the desired package and execute 'makepkg -si'. This will build the package and install it afterwards.